Expand and simplify the expression. [@KeyboardInstructions("Use [|sqrt()|]* for the square root symbol. For example: [`\\sqrt{2}=`][|sqrt(2)|]*.")@]**

    [``\left([$num1] - [$num2] [$sqrt]\right)^2 =``] [__________]{$answer}

END_PGML

